</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-bQtKYq czWvgn pf-23_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-24_ pf-text-1"><strong>Establishment </strong>- Estyn was established in 1992 as an independent organisation tasked with inspecting educational institutions in Wales.

</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-26_ pf-text-1"><strong>Coverage</strong> - Estyn inspects over 1,500 providers annually, including primary and secondary schools, colleges, work-based learning providers, and more.

